---
import "../styles/global.css";
import "../styles/theme.css";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero join-hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Get Involved</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Drive Your Passion Forward</p>
      <a href="https://forms.gle/8zM5WNEvesYNHQ8o8" target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Fill Out the Interest Form
        <span class="arrow-circle"></span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INFO SECTION -->
  <section class="section about">
    <h2>Who We Want</h2>
    <p>
      Whether you're an engineer, designer, business strategist, or simply love racecars, 
      there's a place for you here. We design, build, and compete in Baja SAE. Learning real-world skills along the way.
    </p>

    <h3>Areas You Can Contribute</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Mechanical (Chassis, Suspension, Drivetrain)</li>
      <li>Electrical & Computer (Telemetry, Controls, DAQ)</li>
      <li>Software & Data (Logging, Analysis, UI)</li>
      <li>Business & PR (Sponsorship, Outreach, Branding)</li>
      <li>And more......</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <!-- SAFETY SECTION -->
<!-- JOIN STEPS SECTION -->
<section class="section join-steps">
  <h2>How to Get Involved</h2>
  <p>Follow these steps to gain access to work in our shop where we build the car.</p>

  <!-- Step 1: Safety Trainings -->
  <div class="join-step">
    <h3>Step 1: Complete Required Safety Trainings</h3>
    <p>All members must complete the following online safety courses before working in the shop:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>EOS 029 - Machine Shop Safety</li>
      <li>ELS 002 - Chemical Safety</li>
      <li>ENV 001 - Hazardous Waste</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Steps to complete each course:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Log into <strong>Salute</strong> with your Stony Brook email.</li>
      <li>Under the “Safety Trainings” tab, click <strong>"Go to LMS"</strong>.</li>
      <li>Search for the course (EOS 029, ELS 002, ENV 001), click it, then click <strong>"Enroll Me"</strong>.</li>
      <li>Complete the course material and quiz with at least <strong>80%</strong>.</li>
      <li>Print out the certificate for each course.</li>
      <li>For EOS 029, also print and sign the last page of the Machine Shop Safety Rules & Agreement (leave SBU ID and instructor blank).</li>
      <li>Submit physical copies of all certificates and the signed EOS 029 page to the Motorsports office.</li>
    </ol>

    <a href="https://ehs.stonybrook.edu/resources/sms/index.php" target="_blank" class="btn-secondary">
      Go to Salute LMS
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 2: Interest Form -->
  <div class="join-step">
    <h3>Step 2: Fill Out the Interest Form</h3>
    <p>Once you've completed the safety trainings, fill out the interest form so we can follow up with you.</p>
    <a href="https://forms.gle/8zM5WNEvesYNHQ8o8" target="_blank" class="btn-secondary">
      Fill Out Interest Form
    </a>
  </div>
</section>


</BaseLayout>
